item.title: tuo siht kcehc
item.description: Today I made a dtd. This isn’t really exciting so to speak. But it is quite fun for me. In my head anyway. I really enjoy stupid shit like that. It cracks me up. Last night the phone rang like 5 minutes after I went to sleep.. at like 1:45 or so… and I when I got up to answer the phone I glanced over and noticed a glowing ball of spirits next to my bed.
